description: Had the opportunity to be in the same space with jazz legend Pharoah Sanders, last Friday night, in the green room @ The Pan African Film Festival. Trust... sure wish that I could have found a more quiet environment; a better situation for capturing the video. It's rare though when opportunity & ideal come together as a package. I still cherish the interview. Thank you Mr. Sanders for allowing us to save something for history. I want to thank my friend, Gina Paige of African Ancestry, for posing the questions.
